{"word":"Vinegar","slug":"vinegar","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Vinegar</b> A sour wine.<br/> Forbidden to Nazarites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=6&verse=3'>Num 6:3</a><br/> Used with food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=2&verse=14'>Rth 2:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=69&verse=21'>Psa 69:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=10&verse=26'>Pro 10:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=25&verse=20'>Pro 25:20</a><br/> Offered to Christ on the cross<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=34'>Mat 27:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=48'>Mat 27:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=29'>Joh 19:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=23'>Mar 15:23</a>"}]}